mean_cn: adj. 无比的，无双的，空前的
mean_en: used to emphasize that something is bigger, better or worse than anything else like it
sentence: Your greatness is unparalleled - you're a giant among midgets!
sentence_trans: 你的伟大是无与伦比的——你是矮人中的巨人！
word_etyma: un无 ＋ par比较 ＋ allel其一 ＋ ed...的 → un无 ＋ parallel两者相比=类似的 ＋ ed...的 → unparalleled无比的；空前未有的
